content.text:
Review this Home page with chat response at 325px width (small phone). These are 6 screenshots showing the full page scroll. Check for:
1. Layout overflow - anything extending past viewport?
2. Touch targets - buttons/links at least 44px?
3. Text readability - font sizes adequate?
4. Chat bubble formatting - is the AI response well formatted?
5. Horse cards in the response - are they readable at this width?
6. Input area usability
7. Any visual bugs

Be specific about any issues. Include CSS selectors if possible.
